- **Observed result after fix:** The patched live catalog path returned 36 Copilot models from the real `/models` endpoint. GPT-5.5 is present with live metadata (`contextWindow: 1050000`, `maxTokens: 128000`, reasoning enabled), and Claude Opus 4.7 1M is present with live Anthropic transport, 1M context, xhigh/max compat, and the xhigh thinking map. This confirms the provider catalog can use live entitlement rows instead of the removed bundled/static metadata.
- **What was not tested:** Full built `node openclaw.mjs models list --provider github-copilot` from this source checkout was not completed because `pnpm build` hung in `tsdown` at 0% CPU in this local checkout. The patched Copilot token/catalog modules were exercised directly against the live Copilot service instead.

Maintainer compatibility note: if Copilot live discovery is disabled or token exchange/live `/models` discovery fails, this PR intentionally no longer exposes stale bundled Copilot manifest rows. Explicit user-configured Copilot models remain the fallback/override path.
